        <h2>Boiler Repair vs Replacement - Honest Advice</h2>
        <p>When your boiler breaks down, one of the most important questions is whether it makes financial sense to repair it or replace it with a new one. At Hixa Heating, we pride ourselves on giving honest, transparent advice that's in your best interest, not just what's most profitable for us. We'll never pressure you into an unnecessary boiler replacement if a repair is the sensible option.</p>
        
