        <p>Generally, boiler repairs are the best option when:</p>
        <ul>
            <li><strong>Your boiler is less than 8 years old</strong> - Modern boilers should last 10-15+ years with proper maintenance, so repairs are usually worthwhile for younger units</li>
            <li><strong>The fault is minor</strong> - Simple issues like faulty thermostats, worn seals, or pressure problems are usually quick and inexpensive to fix</li>
